   <body>
      <p>The<uicontrol>Business Unit</uicontrol>formenables you to categorize projectsand users based on the organization's operational functions. Users assigned to a particular business unit can access only projects that are associated with that business unit. You can assign multiple business units to a user and only one business unit to a project.</p>
      <p>The <uicontrol>Business Unit</uicontrol>form enables you to perform the following tasks:<ul>
            <li>
               <xref href="CreateBU.xml">Create a business unit</xref>
            </li>
            <li>
               <xref href="AssignBUtoUser.xml">Assign a business unit to a user</xref>
            </li>
            <li>
               <xref href="RevokeBU.xml">Revoke a business unit from a user</xref>
            </li>
            <li>
               <xref href="DeactBU.xml">Deactivate a business unit</xref>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </p>
